748
01:15:25,750 --> 01:15:27,720
叫保罗·德拉马尔 你认识吗？
His name is Paul Delamare. Do you know him?

749
01:15:27,720 --> 01:15:30,650
不认识 这是我的第一次
No. This is my first time.

750
01:15:30,850 --> 01:15:32,220
第一次飞迪耶普
First time to Dieppe?

751
01:15:32,660 --> 01:15:35,720
是第一次深入敌人后方 长官
First time behind enemy lines ever, sir.

752
01:15:39,000 --> 01:15:41,060
德拉马尔负责着陆地点
Paul Delamare runs the landing sites.

753
01:15:41,060 --> 01:15:43,100
你一眼就能认出他 他缺了一只胳膊
You can't miss him, he only has one arm.

754
01:15:43,270 --> 01:15:45,730
他经常喝酒 但不碍事
He's usually had a few, but he's okay.

755
01:15:45,870 --> 01:15:49,900
你要把这个给他 只能给他 只能给缺一只胳膊的人
I want you to give him this. Give it only to him, only to the man with one arm.

756
01:15:49,910 --> 01:15:51,340
[这是玛丽安·博塞茹尔吗？]
让他给你一个答案
Tell him you need an answer.

757
01:15:51,340 --> 01:15:54,740
[这是玛丽安·博塞茹尔吗？]
简单的是 或不是 仅此而已
A simple oui or non. Only that.

758
01:15:54,750 --> 01:15:55,810
是 长官
Yes, sir.

759
01:15:55,810 --> 01:15:58,980
在电报局等我的电话
Wait for my call in the telegraph office.

760
01:15:58,980 --> 01:16:00,280
我午夜时打给你
I'll call you at midnight.

761
01:16:02,820 --> 01:16:04,420
这是机密
This is classified.

762
01:16:05,020 --> 01:16:06,820
绝不能泄露给任何人 明白吗
No one must know, you understand?

763
01:16:06,820 --> 01:16:07,890
是 长官
Yes, sir.

764
01:16:07,890 --> 01:16:09,290
这事非常重要
It's very important.

765
01:16:10,830 --> 01:16:12,360
请相信我 长官
You can count on me, sir.

766
01:16:13,860 --> 01:16:16,230
迪耶普机场那儿到处都是杨树
The fields in Dieppe are lined with poplar trees.

767
01:16:16,230 --> 01:16:17,870
没月光就看不见
They're invisible if there's no moon,

768
01:16:17,870 --> 01:16:19,030
所以你得快点升空
so climb quickly.

769
01:16:19,040 --> 01:16:20,670
我明白 他们跟我说过情况
I know. I've been briefed.

770
01:16:21,970 --> 01:16:23,040
很好
Good.

771
01:16:24,810 --> 01:16:26,370
你在想谁
Who are you thinking about?

772
01:16:29,110 --> 01:16:30,450
我妈妈
My mother.

773
01:16:30,880 --> 01:16:31,950
别
Don't.

774
01:16:32,110 --> 01:16:33,920
想想你爸爸
Think about your father.

775
01:16:34,380 --> 01:16:36,180
他为你自豪
He's proud of you.

776
01:16:41,860 --> 01:16:43,190
是 长官
Yes, sir.

777
01:16:44,000 --> 01:16:46,860
[玫瑰与王冠]

778
01:17:25,170 --> 01:17:26,970
- 噢  - 抱歉 你请
- Oh.  - Sorry. Go ahead.

779
01:17:26,970 --> 01:17:28,040
谢谢
Thank you.

780
01:17:31,270 --> 01:17:33,810
嗨 比利 两杯白兰地
Hi, Billy. Two brandies.

781
01:17:37,210 --> 01:17:38,350
对不起
Sorry.

782
01:17:40,950 --> 01:17:43,080
我订了三箱苦啤酒
I've ordered three crates of bitter.

783
01:17:43,090 --> 01:17:45,820
黑兹尔 把烟斗洗一下
Hazel, filthy pipe smoke.

784
01:17:48,420 --> 01:17:49,960
谢谢
Thank you.

785
01:17:50,960 --> 01:17:52,760
你拿到威士忌了
Did you get the whiskey?

786
01:17:52,900 --> 01:17:55,030
拿到了 是丘吉尔喝的上等货
I did. Churchill's own.

787
01:17:57,300 --> 01:17:59,030
丈夫会在自己抽烟前
A husband would offer his wife a cigarette...

788
01:17:59,040 --> 01:18:01,370
先给妻子一根烟
before lighting his own.

789
01:18:10,910 --> 01:18:12,980
你确实献了血
You did give blood!

790
01:18:14,250 --> 01:18:15,780
很好
Good.

791
01:18:17,120 --> 01:18:20,050
我以为你跟情妇幽会去了
I thought perhaps you were out with your mistress.

792
01:18:20,920 --> 01:18:23,890
那就能解释你昨晚对我的不同了
It would explain why you were different with me last night.

793
01:18:24,890 --> 01:18:26,060
不同
Different?

794
01:18:27,060 --> 01:18:28,400
在床上
In bed.

795
01:18:29,270 --> 01:18:31,270
感觉不一样
It felt different.

796
01:18:39,240 --> 01:18:40,580
很好
Good.

797
01:18:54,520 --> 01:18:55,860
不好意思
Excuse me!

798
01:18:55,860 --> 01:18:57,190
我们几位特别想看
Me and my mates would really love to see

799
01:18:57,190 --> 01:18:59,930
你们两位女士接吻
you two ladies kiss each other.

800
01:19:03,930 --> 01:19:05,930
真亲了
I don't believe it!

801
01:19:07,470 --> 01:19:09,140
她真够疯的
That was crazy!

802
01:19:23,490 --> 01:19:26,150
马克斯 宴会太棒了
Max, this is splendid.

803
01:19:26,360 --> 01:19:27,960
玛丽安
Marianne!

804
01:19:28,220 --> 01:19:30,890
宴会特别棒 超级棒
Wonderful party! Brilliant!

805
01:19:32,090 --> 01:19:33,630
喝够了吗
Getting enough to drink?

806
01:19:34,000 --> 01:19:35,500
真会说笑 老家伙
Very funny, old man.

807
01:19:37,530 --> 01:19:39,530
不好意思 我家有花园
Hey, excuse me. We have a garden for that.

808
01:19:39,540 --> 01:19:41,500
出去亲热
Take it outside, please.

809
01:19:45,570 --> 01:19:48,540
好了 你们两个 出去亲热
Okay. You two, outside. Outside.

810
01:19:48,550 --> 01:19:50,950
来这儿
Come here.

811
01:19:53,050 --> 01:19:55,480
我的客人表现得太差了
My people are behaving so badly.

812
01:19:55,890 --> 01:19:57,290
我以为他们会吃点东西
I thought they would eat something,

813
01:19:57,290 --> 01:19:59,520
而不是忙着喝酒亲热
not just drink and have sex.

814
01:20:00,460 --> 01:20:02,160
一半的人我都不认识
Half of them I don't even know.

815
01:20:02,160 --> 01:20:04,260
看来汉普斯特这儿的消息传的很快
I think word spread around Hampstead.

816
01:20:04,460 --> 01:20:06,930
这是伦敦 还是战争时期
C'est Londres. C'est la guerre.

817
01:20:10,930 --> 01:20:14,670
你去确认下没人在安娜的房间里乱搞好吗
Would you go check no one is actually fucking in Anna's room?

818
01:20:15,070 --> 01:20:16,240
好
Sure.

819
01:20:29,390 --> 01:20:31,450
马克斯 马克斯 马克斯
Max! Max, Max.

820
01:20:32,120 --> 01:20:33,250
噢 噢
Ooh. Ooh.

821
01:20:33,260 --> 01:20:34,460
对不起
Sorry.

822
01:20:37,390 --> 01:20:38,990
好了
Listen.

823
01:20:39,190 --> 01:20:42,400
听着 他们说你要执行任务
I've been briefed that you're operational,

824
01:20:42,600 --> 01:20:45,470
但是 他们没告诉我是什么任务
but I haven't been told why you're operational.

825
01:20:46,070 --> 01:20:48,200
听着 我觉得作为朋友
Now, look, I thought as a friend

826
01:20:48,200 --> 01:20:51,610
我应该稍微提醒你一下
I ought to just give you a word of warning.

827
01:20:52,610 --> 01:20:54,610
要是V部门给你的任务
If the job V Section are offering you is

828
01:20:54,610 --> 01:20:56,950
就是大家现在说的那个
the one everyone's talking about...

829
01:20:57,280 --> 01:20:59,610
马克斯 如果他们要你在诺曼底登陆日
Max, if they want you to run the resistance...

830
01:20:59,620 --> 01:21:01,350
领导法国抵抗运动
in France on D-Day,

831
01:21:02,080 --> 01:21:03,220
他们不会叫你过去
you should know they wouldn't just call you

832
01:21:03,220 --> 01:21:04,620
搞个面试
in for a job interview.

833
01:21:04,620 --> 01:21:06,720
而是瞒着你考验你
They would test you somehow.

834
01:21:07,490 --> 01:21:08,690
考验
Test?

835
01:21:09,090 --> 01:21:12,630
- 怎么考验  - 这可就大大超出我的安全级别了
- How?  - Way, way above my security clearance, old man.

836
01:21:13,960 --> 01:21:17,200
但是 我要是你 我会坚决拒绝的
But if I were you, I'd tell them to stick their job.

837
01:21:23,570 --> 01:21:25,040
小心 玛格丽特
Careful, Margaret.

838
01:21:40,520 --> 01:21:41,590
马克斯
Max.

839
01:21:42,060 --> 01:21:43,990
我最后还是来了
I was able to make it after all.

840
01:21:44,190 --> 01:21:47,230
弗兰克 没想到你会来
Frank! I didn't expect you.

841
01:21:48,000 --> 01:21:50,670
麻烦你帮忙让这群人冷静点儿吧
Please introduce a little sobriety to the affair.

842
01:21:50,670 --> 01:21:53,070
我可没打算做这种事儿
I wasn't planning on doing anything of the sort.

843
01:21:53,070 --> 01:21:55,000
给我一大杯威士忌和苏打水好吗
A large whiskey and soda, if you please.

844
01:21:55,010 --> 01:21:56,240
去拿酒好吗 亲爱的
Would you get it, honey?

845
01:21:56,240 --> 01:21:58,070
他一脸有事的样子
 Frank still has his work face on.

846
01:21:58,470 --> 01:22:00,610
你养鸡 对不对
You keep chickens, don't you?

847
01:22:01,540 --> 01:22:03,610
弗兰克 你知道得太多了
Frank, you know too much.

848
01:22:03,610 --> 01:22:05,680
带我去看你的鸡 马克斯
Show me your chickens, Max.

849
01:22:22,160 --> 01:22:25,300
你故意而且明目张胆地违抗了命令
You willfully and blatantly disobeyed orders.

850
01:22:25,470 --> 01:22:27,300
先是去找了盖伊·桑斯特
First you visit Guy Sangster

851
01:22:27,300 --> 01:22:28,700
把他气的七窍生烟
and burst half his bloody stitches, then...

852
01:22:28,710 --> 01:22:31,440
弗兰克 要是你的妻子 你能相信V部门吗
Frank, if it was your wife, would you trust V Section?

853
01:22:31,440 --> 01:22:34,480
亚当·亨特的飞机三个小时前被击毁了
Adam Hunter's Lysander was shot to pieces three hours ago.

854
01:22:35,510 --> 01:22:37,510
在着陆点那儿 他在飞机上
On the ground. With him in it!

855
01:22:37,710 --> 01:22:39,380
他死了
He's dead!

856
01:22:40,050 --> 01:22:42,350
就因为他在那儿待得太久了 要从一个醉鬼的
Because he stayed too long waiting for an answer

857
01:22:42,350 --> 01:22:44,550
嘴巴里等到一个答案
to a question from a drunk.

858
01:22:44,750 --> 01:22:47,160
弗兰克 告诉我
Frank, tell me.

859
01:22:47,720 --> 01:22:50,260
- 这是个游戏吗  - 游戏
- Is this a game?  - A game?

860
01:22:50,460 --> 01:22:51,590
游戏
A game.

861
01:22:51,590 --> 01:22:53,130
考验
A test.

862
01:22:55,730 --> 01:22:57,530
我刚刚在跟马克斯说
I was just saying to Max

863
01:22:57,530 --> 01:23:00,800
他在办公室里干得如鱼得水
that he's taken to office life like a duck to water.

864
01:23:03,070 --> 01:23:04,410
我不知道
I wouldn't know.

865
01:23:04,540 --> 01:23:06,140
我很少见到他
I hardly see him.

866
01:23:06,640 --> 01:23:08,710
好了 亲爱的 我们跳舞吧
Come on, honey, let's dance.

867
01:23:19,090 --> 01:23:21,160
弗兰克带了坏消息来？
Frank brought you bad news?

868
01:23:21,760 --> 01:23:23,560
又死了一个飞行员
Another boy dead.

869
01:23:28,100 --> 01:23:30,470
我感觉应该比死人更严重吧
Something more than that, I think.

870
01:23:31,670 --> 01:23:34,140
我问布里奇特你是不是不对劲
I asked Bridget if there was something wrong with you,

871
01:23:34,140 --> 01:23:36,200
她说你没事
and she said you were fine.

872
01:23:37,670 --> 01:23:40,440
她可不像我们这样专门学过骗人
But she's not trained to lie like you and me.

873
01:23:45,810 --> 01:23:48,720
我们有个任务失败了 我不能多说
We've had a setback. I can't talk about it.

874
01:23:54,790 --> 01:23:57,260
烤箱里有东西糊了
I think something's burning in the oven!

875
01:23:57,260 --> 01:23:59,390
好像是俄式炖肉的味道
It could be the stroganoff.

876
01:24:14,580 --> 01:24:16,480
你先退下 上尉
Stand down, Flight Lieutenant.

877
01:24:16,710 --> 01:24:18,510
- 玛格丽特  - 长官
- Margaret?  - Sir.

878
01:24:19,310 --> 01:24:21,150
明天还往迪耶普空投吗
Is the Dieppe drop still on tomorrow?

879
01:24:21,150 --> 01:24:22,680
我想应该会的 长官
I believe it is, sir.

880
01:24:22,690 --> 01:24:25,490
- 天气情况怎么样  - 晴天 长官
- Forecast?  - Clear skies, sir.

881
01:24:53,450 --> 01:24:54,650
嘿
Hey.

882
01:24:56,190 --> 01:24:58,520
那个抽烟斗的 他是谁
The man with the pipe. Who is he?

883
01:24:58,790 --> 01:25:00,450
他叫隆巴德
His name is Lombard.

884
01:25:00,460 --> 01:25:02,660
在商业街上开了家珠宝店
He has a jewelry shop on the high street.

885
01:25:02,660 --> 01:25:05,460
他向我推销一个钻石胸针
He was trying to sell me a diamond broach.

886
01:25:05,660 --> 01:25:07,800
不过我说我们破产了
But I told him we're broke.

887
01:25:10,330 --> 01:25:12,200
你要去哪儿
Hey, where are you going?

888
01:25:12,600 --> 01:25:13,800
- 马克斯  - 玛丽安
- Max!  - Marianne.

889
01:25:13,800 --> 01:25:14,870
我想跟你说点事
I really need to speak to you.

890
01:25:14,870 --> 01:25:16,270
杰弗里 你喝醉了
Oh. Jeffrey, you're too drunk.

891
01:25:24,550 --> 01:25:25,610
嘿
Hey.

892
01:25:28,880 --> 01:25:30,950
你的妻子改主意了
Your wife changed her mind.

893
01:25:31,690 --> 01:25:33,590
你说的是耳环吗
You mean about the earrings.

894
01:25:34,560 --> 01:25:37,490
不不不 我想卖给她的是胸针
No, no, no, I was trying to sell her a broach.

895
01:25:37,760 --> 01:25:39,560
不过我确实有些漂亮的耳环
I do have some beautiful earrings.

896
01:25:39,560 --> 01:25:41,300
而且可以给你个优惠价
I can offer you a very good price.

897
01:25:41,430 --> 01:25:42,560
马克斯
Max.

898
01:25:43,830 --> 01:25:47,500
不用了 隆巴德先生 我们真的破产了
It's okay, Mr. Lombard. We really are broke.

899
01:25:49,500 --> 01:25:50,840
晚安
Good night.

900
01:25:51,370 --> 01:25:52,370
晚安
Good night.

901
01:26:10,460 --> 01:26:12,390
我去看看安娜
I'll have to get Anna.

902
01:26:22,540 --> 01:26:24,940
- 我没听到警报  - 警报怎么没响
- I didn't hear a siren.  - Where were the sirens?

903
01:26:27,480 --> 01:26:28,980
总算响了
Now they sound the alarm.

904
01:26:28,980 --> 01:26:31,480
这什么警报啊 总是慢两拍
Bloody ARP, always two steps behind.

905
01:26:31,680 --> 01:26:34,280
赶快把灯给关掉
Get these bloody lights off!

906
01:26:42,290 --> 01:26:44,360
他们又轰炸东区了
They're targeting the East End again.

907
01:26:46,960 --> 01:26:48,960
这一片应该没事
We should be all right here.

908
01:26:49,830 --> 01:26:52,030
马克斯 别再搞事了
Max, no more.

909
01:26:52,830 --> 01:26:54,370
拜托
Please?

910
01:26:55,640 --> 01:26:57,570
到星期一上午
By Monday morning, we'll...

911
01:26:57,570 --> 01:26:59,570
我们就知道结果了
We'll know for sure.

912
01:27:01,310 --> 01:27:03,080
去休息一下吧
Try and get some rest.

913
01:27:05,310 --> 01:27:07,650
- 弗兰克  - 这不是游戏
- Frank?  - It's not a game.

914
01:27:10,350 --> 01:27:11,820
就算它是
Even if it is,

915
01:27:13,620 --> 01:27:15,620
V部门也不会告诉你的
V Section wouldn't tell you.

916
01:27:15,630 --> 01:27:17,090
对不对
Would they?

917
01:27:20,500 --> 01:27:22,430
他们不会告诉你的 弗兰克
They wouldn't tell you, Frank.

918
01:27:29,000 --> 01:27:30,370
看
Look!

919
01:27:30,370 --> 01:27:32,570
击落一架 好耶
We got one! Yes!

920
01:27:56,500 --> 01:27:57,830
飞机朝我们这边来了
It's heading right towards us!

921
01:27:57,830 --> 01:27:59,570
大家快找掩护
Everyone take cover!

922
01:28:02,900 --> 01:28:04,110
蹲下
Get down!

923
01:28:08,540 --> 01:28:09,610
马克斯
Max!

924
01:28:36,570 --> 01:28:38,510
你去让大家散了好吗
Will you get rid of everyone?

925
01:28:39,710 --> 01:28:40,880
好
Yeah.

926
01:28:46,480 --> 01:28:47,680
马克斯
Max.

927
01:28:50,950 --> 01:28:53,620
明天我们能陪安娜一整天
Tomorrow we have a whole day with Anna.

928
01:28:56,120 --> 01:28:57,930
我们忘记战争
Let's forget the war.

929
01:29:00,460 --> 01:29:02,660
好好地度过这一天吧
Let's make the best day ever.

930
01:29:04,700 --> 01:29:05,770
好
Yeah.

931
01:29:07,470 --> 01:29:08,940
我很愿意
I'd like that.

932
01:30:25,510 --> 01:30:27,820
谁要先跳呀
Who's gonna jump first?

933
01:30:29,920 --> 01:30:32,720
我生火了 过来跟我们一起坐吧
I've lit a fire. Come sit with us.

934
01:30:32,950 --> 01:30:34,150
这个吗
This one?

935
01:31:07,690 --> 01:31:09,060
空军上尉
Flight Lieutenant!

936
01:31:09,720 --> 01:31:12,660
我有个好消息 今晚可以休息了
I have good news. You have the night off.

937
01:31:12,790 --> 01:31:13,930
是 长官
Yes, sir.

938
01:33:05,690 --> 01:33:08,060
你在干什么 为什么把引擎关了
What the hell are you doing? Why have you switched off the engine?

939
01:33:08,260 --> 01:33:09,690
保罗·德拉马尔在哪儿
Where is Paul Delamare?

940
01:33:10,540 --> 01:33:11,540
保罗·德拉马尔
Paul Delamare ??

941
01:33:11,710 --> 01:33:13,530
- 他进监狱了  - 什么
- He's in jail.  - What?

942
01:33:13,830 --> 01:33:15,400
德拉马尔 他进监狱了
Delamare is in jail.

943
01:33:15,600 --> 01:33:16,780
什么 是盖世太保抓的
What? Gestapo?

944
01:33:17,580 --> 01:33:19,100
不 警察抓的
No, local police.

945
01:33:19,850 --> 01:33:21,480
他又喝醉了
Drunk as usual.

946
01:33:24,930 --> 01:33:26,250
带我去监狱
Take me to the jail.

947
01:33:34,650 --> 01:33:35,350
我们走
Let’s go

948
01:33:57,470 --> 01:33:58,630
里面有多少警察
How many inside?

949
01:33:58,830 --> 01:34:00,430
今晚只有一个
This time of night, only one.

950
01:34:28,910 --> 01:34:30,470
求求你别杀我
I don't want any trouble!

951
01:34:31,960 --> 01:34:33,690
保罗·德拉马尔在哪儿
Where is Paul Delamare?

952
01:34:34,490 --> 01:34:35,750
三号牢房
Cell number three.

953
01:34:41,750 --> 01:34:43,450
- 你在这儿看着他  - 没问题
- You're here to see him.  - no problem

954
01:34:45,560 --> 01:34:47,460
求求你别杀我
I don't want any trouble.

955
01:34:50,260 --> 01:34:51,060
去后面守着
Go back and watch

956
01:35:07,300 --> 01:35:08,300
打开
Open it.

957
01:35:13,000 --> 01:35:14,400
该死 该死的 怎么回事
Damn it, damn it. What's going on?

958
01:35:14,740 --> 01:35:18,150
不好意思 德拉马尔先生 我在赶时间
I'm sorry, Mr. Delamare. I'm in a hurry.

959
01:35:19,280 --> 01:35:22,150
接下来我要说的是最高机密 最高机密
What I'm going to say is top secret.

960
01:35:24,240 --> 01:35:27,300
- 你懂英语吗  - 不懂 怎么了
- Do you speak English?   - No. Why?

961
01:35:27,500 --> 01:35:28,000
这到底怎么回事
What the hell is going on here?

962
01:35:28,950 --> 01:35:31,120
看 你看 仔细看
Look. Look closely.

963
01:35:31,320 --> 01:35:33,850
照片上的这个女人是玛丽安·博塞茹尔吗
Is the woman in this photograph Marianne Beauséjour?

964
01:35:33,860 --> 01:35:34,990
谁
Who?

965
01:35:35,460 --> 01:35:37,260
玛丽安·博塞茹尔
Marianne Beauséjour!

966
01:35:41,030 --> 01:35:42,300
看着 是她吗
Look! Is it her?

967
01:35:45,000 --> 01:35:46,430
酒 把酒瓶给我
Give me the bottle!

968
01:35:46,440 --> 01:35:48,200
回答我 我就给你酒瓶
Yes or no, and then you get a drink.

969
01:35:48,200 --> 01:35:49,500
玛丽安·博塞茹尔
Marianne Beauséjour?

970
01:35:49,510 --> 01:35:51,000
玛丽安·博塞茹尔
Marianne Beauséjour.

971
01:35:51,010 --> 01:35:53,140
玛丽安·博塞茹尔
Marianne Beauséjour...

972
01:35:53,410 --> 01:35:54,610
看着
Look!

973
01:35:58,010 --> 01:36:00,250
是 是她
Yes. It's her.

974
01:36:00,250 --> 01:36:02,020
- 是吗  - 把酒瓶给我
- Yes?  - Now let me have a drink.

975
01:36:02,020 --> 01:36:03,380
再看看 你确定
Look again. Are you sure?

976
01:36:03,390 --> 01:36:05,220
去你的
Fuck you!

977
01:36:06,020 --> 01:36:07,220
看着 看着
Look. Look!

978
01:36:07,420 --> 01:36:09,420
- 这个女人就是她  - 是吗
- She look the same. Yeah.  - Yes?

979
01:36:09,430 --> 01:36:11,490
她喜欢笑 棕色头发
She laughs a lot. Brown hair.

980
01:36:11,490 --> 01:36:14,160
- 棕色眼睛 对吗  - 对 棕色眼睛
- And she has brown eyes, yes?  - Right. Brown eyes.

981
01:36:14,160 --> 01:36:16,430
她是蓝眼睛 混蛋 是蓝眼睛
She's got blue eyes! God damn it, blue eyes!

982
01:36:16,430 --> 01:36:18,070
对 对 我就是说蓝眼睛
Right! I mean blue.

983
01:36:18,070 --> 01:36:19,130
别耍我 德拉马尔
Don't you fuck with me, Delamare.

984
01:36:19,130 --> 01:36:21,030
我之前说错了
I made a mistake.

985
01:36:21,040 --> 01:36:23,900
- 看着  - 她的眼睛是蓝的
- Look!  - She has blue eyes.

986
01:36:24,310 --> 01:36:27,110
我认识她 真的
I know her. Sure.

987
01:36:28,180 --> 01:36:30,980
她是聚会上的焦点
She is the life of the party.

988
01:36:31,580 --> 01:36:32,910
继续
Go on.

989
01:36:33,250 --> 01:36:35,250
她会画画
And she paints.

990
01:36:36,050 --> 01:36:37,920
画画 对 她画什么
Paints, yes. She paints what?

991
01:36:38,320 --> 01:36:40,650
她画的水彩画 非常美
Wonderful watercolors.

992
01:36:41,520 --> 01:36:42,590
没错
That's right.

993
01:36:42,990 --> 01:36:44,990
- 把酒给我  - 没问题
- Give me the bottle.  - That's right.

994
01:36:45,600 --> 01:36:46,600
德国佬
The Krauts!

995
01:36:47,130 --> 01:36:51,430
她弹钢琴的样子宛如女神
And she plays the piano like a goddess.

996
01:36:53,470 --> 01:36:54,940
钢琴
Piano?

997
01:37:09,670 --> 01:37:10,680
别动
Don't move.

998
01:37:15,500 --> 01:37:18,200
朋友们 谁想抽点美国香烟
Who wants some American cigarettes?

999
01:37:21,160 --> 01:37:22,230
嘿
Hey!

1000
01:37:22,460 --> 01:37:23,530
什么
Quoi?

1001
01:37:23,640 --> 01:37:25,840
德国佬有时候会过来
Sometimes the Krauts...

1002
01:37:26,440 --> 01:37:28,380
找我们要美国香烟
...they come to get American cigarettes.

1003
01:37:28,580 --> 01:37:29,800
什么美国香烟
American cigarettes?

1004
01:37:30,690 --> 01:37:32,700
我们从反抗军那没收的
We confiscate them from the Resistance.

1005
01:37:33,240 --> 01:37:35,140
我记得玛丽安
I remember Marianne.

1006
01:37:36,580 --> 01:37:38,650
我第一次遇见她
I remember when I met her.

1007
01:37:39,580 --> 01:37:42,980
是在多尔多涅的一个咖啡馆
It was in a café. In Dordogne.

1008
01:37:43,580 --> 01:37:46,650
咖啡馆里有一群德国士兵
The place was full of German soldiers.

1009
01:37:47,420 --> 01:37:48,890
- 我们得走了  - 等等 等等
- We gotta go!  - Wait!

1010
01:37:49,590 --> 01:37:51,660
里面有一架钢琴
There was a piano.

1011
01:37:52,530 --> 01:37:54,390
她走了过去
She went to it

1012
01:37:54,600 --> 01:37:56,600
弹奏了《马赛曲》
and played La Marseillaise

1013
01:37:57,000 --> 01:37:59,970
就在那些德国佬的面前
in front of all those Germans!

1014
01:38:01,050 --> 01:38:03,750
出发吧 祖国的孩子们
Set out, the children of the motherland

1015
01:38:05,850 --> 01:38:06,650
闭嘴 闭嘴
Shut up, shut up

1016
01:38:23,290 --> 01:38:24,160
皮埃尔
Hey, Pierre!

1017
01:38:25,290 --> 01:38:26,640
好彩香烟
Lucky Strike?

1018
01:38:26,740 --> 01:38:27,540
快点开门
Open the door

1019
01:38:28,880 --> 01:38:30,450
你有那烟吗
Do you have the cigarettes?

1020
01:38:30,950 --> 01:38:32,220
把烟给他
Give them to him.

1021
01:38:37,270 --> 01:38:39,210
喂 皮埃尔
Allo, Pierre?

1022
01:38:40,140 --> 01:38:41,440
皮埃尔 是我
Pierre, c'est moi!

1023
01:38:43,520 --> 01:38:44,120
开门 开门
Open the door

1024
01:38:51,220 --> 01:38:52,020
游击队
Guerrilla detachment

1025
01:38:56,320 --> 01:38:57,120
游击队
Guerrilla detachment

1026
01:39:04,430 --> 01:39:05,960
监狱后面
Behind the jail!

1027
01:39:06,160 --> 01:39:08,610
是游击队的人 他们往后面跑了
The Resistance are running behind the jail!

1028
01:39:09,410 --> 01:39:11,440
德国佬在广场上
The Krauts are in the square!

1029
01:39:12,960 --> 01:39:14,300
给我个手榴弹
A grenade.

1030
01:39:15,100 --> 01:39:16,400
这里 从这个门走
Here, walk through the door

1031
01:40:50,440 --> 01:40:51,610
玛丽安
Marianne,

1032
01:40:53,540 --> 01:40:55,640
你跟我出去一趟
I need you to come with me.

1033
01:40:59,410 --> 01:41:02,480
把安娜交给保姆 你现在跟我出去
Drop off Anna and come with me now, please.

1034
01:41:09,720 --> 01:41:11,790
你到底在做什么
What the hell are you doing?

1035
01:41:30,210 --> 01:41:31,410
玛丽安
Marianne...

1036
01:41:35,620 --> 01:41:37,950
我想听你给我弹钢琴
I want you to play the piano for me.

1037
01:41:39,590 --> 01:41:41,390
你想什么
You want what?

1038
01:41:43,190 --> 01:41:46,260
你为什么突然要我弹钢琴
Why on earth would you want me to play the piano?

1039
01:41:48,500 --> 01:41:51,300
我想让你弹钢琴 因为我爱你
I want you to play the piano because I love you.

1040
01:41:54,340 --> 01:41:56,540
你到底在说什么
What are you talking about?

1041
01:41:56,740 --> 01:41:59,540
你熬了一夜 我们回家吧
You haven't slept. Let's go home.

1042
01:42:07,750 --> 01:42:10,320
我想听你弹《马赛曲》
I want you to play La Marseillaise.

1043
01:42:14,260 --> 01:42:17,460
虽然你以前也让我做过奇奇怪怪的事
Now, you have asked me some strange things...

1044
01:42:17,660 --> 01:42:18,860
弹
Play.

1045
01:42:29,540 --> 01:42:32,970
玛丽安·博塞茹尔一九四一年在一家咖啡馆里
Marianne Beauséjour played La Marseillaise

1046
01:42:33,670 --> 01:42:36,580
当着德国人的面弹了《马赛曲》
in a café full of Germans in '41.

1047
01:42:37,780 --> 01:42:39,850
我想听你给我弹
I want you to play it for me.

1048
01:43:12,550 --> 01:43:14,480
我知道这件事
I know the story.

1049
01:43:16,720 --> 01:43:19,350
她是一个非常勇敢的女人
She was a very brave woman.

1050
01:43:24,590 --> 01:43:27,360
我以为他们找不到我了
I thought they wouldn't find me here.

1051
01:43:27,560 --> 01:43:29,030
可他们找到了
But they did.

1052
01:43:29,460 --> 01:43:31,530
他们拿安娜威胁我
And they threatened Anna.

1053
01:43:31,730 --> 01:43:34,800
我 我真的很抱歉
And I'm... And I'm so sorry.

1054
01:43:37,340 --> 01:43:38,740
我真的很抱歉
I am so sorry.

1055
01:43:41,710 --> 01:43:43,380
你发了吗
Did you send it?

1056
01:43:45,010 --> 01:43:47,410
那条情报你发了吗
The message! Did you send it?

1057
01:43:49,620 --> 01:43:50,680
发了
Yes.

1058
01:44:01,330 --> 01:44:03,060
对不起
I'm sorry.

1059
01:44:07,500 --> 01:44:08,970
你告诉我
I need to know,

1060
01:44:09,470 --> 01:44:10,940
这是真的吗
is this real?

1061
01:44:12,470 --> 01:44:13,670
你爱我吗
Do you love me?

1062
01:44:14,810 --> 01:44:17,010
我爱你 我爱你
I love you. I love you.

1063
01:44:17,880 --> 01:44:20,910
我在卡萨布兰卡就爱上了你
I've loved you since Casablanca.

1064
01:44:29,060 --> 01:44:31,990
好了 听我说 我们接下来这样做
Okay, listen to me. This is how it will be.

1065
01:44:32,630 --> 01:44:34,790
我们一起去梅迪辛哈特
There is a Medicine Hat

1066
01:44:34,800 --> 01:44:37,630
它就在瑞士 或者秘鲁 或者管它在什么鬼地方
in Switzerland or Peru or wherever the hell.

1067
01:44:37,630 --> 01:44:39,500
我们去不了的
We won't make it.

1068
01:44:39,500 --> 01:44:43,440
再过一个小时 V部门就会让我杀了你
If we stay one more hour, V Section's gonna order me to kill you.

1069
01:44:43,940 --> 01:44:46,710
如果我不答应 我们俩都会死
And when I refuse, they're gonna shoot us both.

1070
01:44:46,940 --> 01:44:48,480
明白吗
You understand?

1071
01:44:49,640 --> 01:44:50,980
我们现在就走
We go now.

1072
01:44:55,050 --> 01:44:57,120
我们得去接安娜
We have to get Anna.

1073
01:45:08,700 --> 01:45:10,460
玛丽安呢
Where is Marianne?

1074
01:45:13,970 --> 01:45:16,470
你拿我的孩子当人质
You used my child as collateral.

1075
01:45:18,570 --> 01:45:22,540
你也毫不逊色 瓦坦中校
You've done far worse, Wing Commander Vatan.

1076
01:45:22,680 --> 01:45:24,540
还有谁在监视我们
Who else is watching us?

1077
01:45:24,550 --> 01:45:27,810
我是第三帝国的特工
Ich bin einen agent des Reiches.

1078
01:45:29,680 --> 01:45:31,150
我只能告诉你我的…
I will only give you my...

1079
01:45:36,560 --> 01:45:37,820
过来 别怕 宝贝儿
Come here, sweetheart.

1080
01:45:38,860 --> 01:45:42,600
别怕 宝贝儿 别怕 没事了
It's okay, honey. It's okay. It's okay.

1081
01:45:57,500 --> 01:46:00,200
[隆巴德珠宝]

1082
01:48:13,110 --> 01:48:15,920
好 长官 您可以过去了
Very good, sir. You're free to pass.

1083
01:49:01,160 --> 01:49:02,700
在这儿等着
Wait here.

1084
01:50:47,840 --> 01:50:49,470
结束了 马克斯！
It's over, Max!

1085
01:50:52,910 --> 01:50:54,270
蓝色染料程序证明她是间谍
The blue-dye came back positive.

1086
01:50:54,280 --> 01:50:56,240
你已经知道了 是不是
But you already know that, don't you?

1087
01:50:56,240 --> 01:50:57,340
弗兰克 等等
Frank, wait!

1088
01:50:57,880 --> 01:51:00,180
等等 你听我解释
Wait! Let me explain.

1089
01:51:00,380 --> 01:51:03,080
- 我已经清除了其他潜伏间谍  - 马克斯·瓦坦
- The circuit's been cleaned.  - Max Vatan,

1090
01:51:03,380 --> 01:51:05,850
以国王陛下乔治六世之名
in the name of His Majesty King George VI...

1091
01:51:05,850 --> 01:51:07,250
是他们逼她的 弗兰克
They had her boxed in, Frank!

1092
01:51:07,260 --> 01:51:09,020
我宣判你犯了叛国罪
I charge you with high treason...

1093
01:51:09,020 --> 01:51:10,290
不 求你了
No! Please!

1094
01:51:10,290 --> 01:51:12,460
协助并教唆德国间谍
...for aiding and abetting the German spy

1095
01:51:12,460 --> 01:51:14,390
玛丽安·博塞茹尔
known as Marianne Beauséjour.

1096
01:51:14,400 --> 01:51:18,130
弗兰克 她是被逼的 他们拿安娜 拿我们全家威胁她
Frank, she had no choice. They threatened Anna. They would have killed us all!

1097
01:51:18,130 --> 01:51:19,330
马克斯 你已经疯了吗
Max, have you lost your mind?

1098
01:51:19,330 --> 01:51:20,770
她是德国间谍
She's a German spy!

1099
01:51:20,770 --> 01:51:22,170
我不会让你动她的 弗兰克
I won't let you do this, Frank.

1100
01:51:22,170 --> 01:51:24,170
我的任务完成了 我杀了潜伏间谍
I've done my duty. We've cleaned up the circuit.

1101
01:51:24,170 --> 01:51:26,170
该死 他们掌握了重要情报
They had valuable information, damn you!

1102
01:51:26,170 --> 01:51:28,310
她是被逼的 他们要杀安娜
She had no choice! They threatened Anna!

1103
01:51:28,310 --> 01:51:30,240
如果你不想被处决
If you want to walk away from this,

1104
01:51:31,180 --> 01:51:33,950
你知道应该怎么做
then do what needs to be done.

1105
01:51:33,950 --> 01:51:35,950
她是被逼的 德国人威胁她
She had no choice. They had her boxed in.

1106
01:51:35,950 --> 01:51:37,350
拿我们全家人的性命威胁她
They would've killed us all.

1107
01:51:37,950 --> 01:51:39,290
V部门才不管这个
The Section won't care.

1108
01:51:39,290 --> 01:51:40,890
他们要杀安娜
They threatened Anna!

1109
01:51:40,890 --> 01:51:43,960
为了你的孩子 不要自己找死
For your child's sake, don't throw your life away!

1110
01:51:43,960 --> 01:51:46,030
我完成任务了 你让开
We did our duty. Just walk away.

1111
01:51:46,030 --> 01:51:47,190
让开 弗兰克
Walk away, Frank.

1112
01:51:47,200 --> 01:51:48,260
马克斯
Max.

1113
01:51:53,930 --> 01:51:56,270
我爱你 我的魁北瓜
Je t'aime, mon Québécois.

1114
01:52:00,470 --> 01:52:02,110
我爱你
I love you.

1115
01:52:05,080 --> 01:52:07,110
好好照顾她
Take good care of her.

1116
01:53:19,950 --> 01:53:21,330
解除戒备
Stand down.

1117
01:53:24,060 --> 01:53:28,130
空军中校马克斯·瓦坦亲手处决了敌方间谍
Wing Commander Vatan executed the enemy agent with his own hand.

1118
01:53:30,530 --> 01:53:32,670
你们就这么报告
That is how you will report it.

1119
01:53:33,930 --> 01:53:35,530
这是命令
That is an order.

1120
01:54:18,250 --> 01:54:21,180
我亲爱的安娜宝贝儿
My dearest, darling Anna.

1121
01:54:27,960 --> 01:54:31,290
我在一个星期日的晚上 在伦敦写下了这封信
I'm writing this on a Sunday night in London.

1122
01:54:34,260 --> 01:54:36,330
当你读到这封信时
If you're reading this,

1123
01:54:36,530 --> 01:54:38,560
也许你会对我感到陌生
then you barely knew me

1124
01:54:39,100 --> 01:54:41,470
也许根本想不起来我是谁
and may have no memory of who I am.

1125
01:54:43,500 --> 01:54:45,470
我是你的妈妈
I am your mother.

1126
01:54:47,010 --> 01:54:50,210
你出生在战争时期的一次空袭中
You were born in an air raid in the middle of a war

1127
01:54:51,140 --> 01:54:54,050
是爸爸妈妈的爱情结晶
to two people who loved each other.

1128
01:54:56,650 --> 01:54:59,520
我们在汉普斯特的这栋房子里
Our year together in the house in Hampstead

1129
01:54:59,520 --> 01:55:01,990
度过的一年是我一生中最幸福的时光
has been the happiest time of my life.

1130
01:55:09,300 --> 01:55:11,730
今天 你学会了走路
Today you took your first steps.

1131
01:55:16,140 --> 01:55:19,270
我很感激有你爸爸陪在我身边
I am so grateful that I saw you walk for the first time

1132
01:55:19,270 --> 01:55:21,370
看到你第一次走路
with your father by my side.

1133
01:55:25,050 --> 01:55:26,780
马克斯 我的爱人
Max, my love,

1134
01:55:28,720 --> 01:55:30,650
你就是我的世界
you are my world.

1135
01:55:36,590 --> 01:55:39,630
我希望你能够原谅我
I hope you will be able to forgive me.

1136
01:55:41,460 --> 01:55:44,230
我希望你能去梅迪辛哈特
And I hope you make it to Medicine Hat.

1137
01:55:48,340 --> 01:55:50,800
我在脑海里想象过它的样子
I have a picture of it in my mind,

1138
01:55:51,740 --> 01:55:54,770
我希望安娜能亲眼看到它
and I pray Anna's eyes will see it.

1139
01:55:58,750 --> 01:56:00,810
我可爱的女儿
My beautiful daughter,

1140
01:56:02,350 --> 01:56:04,680
我全心全意地爱着你
I love you with all my heart.

1141
01:56:08,220 --> 01:56:11,160
我希望你这一生能平平安安的
I hope you will live your life in peace.

1142
01:56:13,360 --> 01:56:17,830
我知道你爸爸会好好照顾你的 这样我就能安息了
I rest knowing your father will take good care of you.

1143
01:56:23,140 --> 01:56:25,470
永远爱你的妈妈
I remain your loving mother,

1144
01:56:27,670 --> 01:56:29,480
玛丽安·瓦坦
Marianne Vatan.
